	(463, 100, 'sa_slide1_content', '<h5><img class="size-full wp-image-89 alignnone" src="http://orchidee.test/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Screen-Shot-2022-09-15-at-13.04-1.png" alt="" width="251" height="239" /></h5>\r\n<div class="mceTemp" style="text-align: center"> </div>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center">Yuniza icha </h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">Artist, DJ</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><br /> “My first impression at the orchidee clinic is that the staffs was so nice, the therapist was also very friendly and knew what the client needed. Also, this place is very comfortable and spacious. I tried soft laser and HiTech facial there is no pain and immediately see the results. I highly recommend, you have to try it”</p>'),
